title: FS2004 - FSfreeware Las Vegas Photorealistic
description:
FSfreeware Las Vegas Photorealistic - Repack & Re-release By 108

Since I&#039;ve never seen this posted anywhere, I assume this is fairly a hard-to-find scenery. I&#039;ve thoroughly enjoyed it over the years, and thought I&#039;d share it with you. It&#039;s not perfect, but it&#039;s the only KLAS photoscenery I&#039;ve ever seen.

I use it in conjunction with some photoscenery extentions i&#039;ve been developing, which cover areas south, from Boulder City to Jean, Sandy Valley to the southwest, & the Spring Mountains to the west, including Mt. Charleston. I hope to release these soon, as they really add an amazing level of realism to the area, but for now you&#039;ve got some photoreal Las Vegas airspace to fly around in. :-)

Enjoy!
